{"tid":116483,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"陶傑食熱狗話政治冇倫理，bb班先講政治倫理，大家點睇？","createTime":"2017-02-11T12:38:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-14T15:32:42.000Z","uid":30807,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c5d052597fae947eede31d6c2d1e221899278c5e","tid":116483,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T12:38:33.000Z","msg":"2017年2月9號晚，光明頂節目<br />\n<br />\n陶傑：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陶傑：政治係不講邏輯，亦係冇倫理，甚至係亂倫，反倫理，六親不認。<br />\n<br />\n冇錯，政治要講現實，同埋講利益。<br />\n<br />\n所以有d人士呢，係香港講話從政從政幾廿年呢都未開竅，幼稚園bb班未畢業就係咁解。<br />\n<br />\n對於某d年輕人，某一種選民黎講，呢d係一種魅力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(以上為文字節錄，中間有刪減部份，強烈建議自行聽節目一次)<br />\n<br />\n熱普城：本民青冇政治倫理！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  陶傑<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  熱普城"},{"pid":"55faf26dd8fd02cf38f15eb4939649915cb20705","tid":116483,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T12:56:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16691db3a69c13db4be0f1db400a7d0a38382417","tid":116483,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T01:53:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"814b4dfbfaf8172ec30a932e4a9ad392bfdf83ea","tid":116483,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T02:03:30.000Z","msg":"個人認為<br />\n市民制益&gt;倫理&gt;個人利益"},{"pid":"e8535080701a372ba96685d1187b1c4c3494122d","tid":116483,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T05:20:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個人認為<br />\n市民制益&gt;倫理&gt;個人利益</blockquote><br />\n快啲移民去西方國家住幾年你就會明白"},{"pid":"8e63d4ebe7e841bd32817981e371a29562cc6520","tid":116483,"uid":13948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T05:22:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個人認為<br />\n市民制益&gt;倫理&gt;個人利益</blockquote><br />\n<br />\